  "title": "Assistant Workshop Supervisor (Golf Club)-6681",
  "description": "<p><strong>Assistant Operation Supervisor (Golf Club)</strong></p><p><strong>Salary</strong>: <strong>$3000-$3400 + AWS + bonus</strong></p><p><strong>Working Hours: 5.5Days Work week : Monday :6.30am -3.45pm , Tues - Friday 6.30am - 2.45pm</strong></p><p><strong>Sat or Sunday 6.30-12.15pm</strong></p><p><strong>Location:  Tanah Merah Coast Road</strong></p><h2><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Oversee day-to-day workshop operations, ensuring safety, efficiency, and compliance.</p></li><li><p>Plan and monitor workloads, supervise mechanics, and manage workshop resources.</p></li><li><p>Prepare and implement scheduled maintenance programs for all machinery and buggies.</p></li><li><p>Maintain quality control through inspections of parts and assemblies.</p></li><li><p>Ensure proper upkeep of golf course machines, irrigation pump house machinery, and club vehicles.</p></li><li><p>Keep machinery tournament-ready for all events.</p></li><li><p>Manage budgets for materials and resources, and support operational planning</p></li></ul><p>Requirement</p><ul><li><p>2years of relevant experience in the golfing industry or similar mechanical workshop environment</p></li></ul><p>CHUAH ZHI XING | Reg No: R25136681</p><p>THE SUPREME HR ADVISORY PTE LTD | EA No: 14C7279</p>",
